{"tid":2155681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人權領袖轟華圖操控世界","createTime":"2020-08-14T03:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T03:20:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83d37ec4d8d8b084c38858747b906270ae3f6d1a","tid":2155681,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/IQ7LP4FBNRG75OORJQD53YT4JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FIQ7LP4FBNRG75OORJQD53YT4JU%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=68bfecb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FIQ7LP4FBNRG75OORJQD53YT4JU%2F&h=3f1a7f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/IQ7LP4FBNRG75OORJQD53YT4JU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n人權領袖轟華圖操控世界<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NnXWgsMPm01DvjgD2C_wO3Q9kPA=/874x607/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EUGY6FYYXZEHDCLWHFLRUESZ4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNnXWgsMPm01DvjgD2C_wO3Q9kPA%3D%2F874x607%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEUGY6FYYXZEHDCLWHFLRUESZ4U.jpg&h=c422af87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■自由之家主席阿布拉莫維茨（圓圖）撰文指對中方制裁感迷惘。<br />\n<br />\n周初遭中國制裁的國際人權監察組織「自由之家」主席阿布拉莫維茨（Mike Abramowitz）在美國《大西洋雜誌》撰文，形容中共是「在海外綁架異見分子」的政權，圖操控美國以至全世界人的言行，美國必須制止，「我們有義務支持其他地方的民主進程」。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，在香港出生的他，相信自己再不能回港。"},{"pid":"6f80b99f57158614f20dcf77238496c6c7e2d1a7","tid":2155681,"uid":124983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"原來係香港出生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}